#. translators: Please don't forget the rel=nofollow element in the link - it makes sure we don't increase MS PR.
#: lib/views/windows.restrictions.php:65
msgid ""
"Companies like Microsoft like to assimilate their software to physical "
"products, <a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/piracy/\" rel=\"nofollow\">when "
"mentioning copyright infringement</a> for example. Yet, proprietary software "
"is very different because of the restrictive license -such restrictions "
"would be unthinkable on a car or bicycle, for example."
msgstr ""
"像是微軟這類的公司每當提及<a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/piracy/\" rel="
"\"nofollow\">盜版、侵權</a>之時，就會將他們的軟體比擬作實際的有形硬體產品。然"
"而，專有軟體因為具有充滿限制的授權條款卻顯得格格不入 ─ 諸如此類的限制若發生在"
"車子或是腳踏車上簡直是無法想像。"

#: lib/views/windows.restrictions.php:66
msgid ""
"Restrictions on the use of Office and Windows are so harsh, that many "
"violations occur everyday around us. People are tempted to buy only one "
"version of Microsoft Office and install it on two computers. Others keep "
"their version of Windows when they throw their PC away. Other people give "
"away their second-hand Windows software when they stop using it."
msgstr ""
"使用 Office 及 Windows 的限制是非常嚴苛的，所以許多侵權事件在現實生活中經常發"
"生。人們總是抵不住只購買一份微軟 Office 的授權，然後再安裝到兩臺電腦上的誘"
"惑。有些人則是在丟棄了他們的舊電腦後卻又保留原先的副本拷貝。還有一些則是在他"
"們不使用之後卻又轉讓二手的 Windows 軟體出去。"

#. translators: use the definition of "free software" on GNU.org in place of softwareliberty.com ; also, if you can, use a translation of the GPL as found on http://www.gnu.org/licenses/translations.html
#: lib/views/windows.restrictions.php:69
msgid ""
"<strong>You have an alternative to breaking this law,</strong> or feeling "
"very restrained when you abide to it. GNU/Linux is <a href=\"http://www."
"softwareliberty.com/\">Free Software</a> (much better than just freeware): "
"its <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html\">GPL</a> license is "
"designed to protect your rights."
msgstr ""
"<strong>其實你有除了違法以外的另一個選擇，</strong>或是如果你也對忍受繁多的規"
"定感到處處受限 ─ GNU/Linux 可是<a href=\"http://www.softwareliberty.com/\">自"
"由軟體</a> (遠比免費軟體好太多了)：它使用 <a href=\"http://www.linux.org.tw/"
"CLDP/OLD/doc/GPL.html\">GPL</a> 授權條款來保障你的權利。"

